---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Contact" description="Ways to reach out about Evie's creative work." currentPath="/contact">
  <section class="page-intro panel">
    <p class="eyebrow">Contact</p>
    <h1>Share gently, invite thoughtfully.</h1>
    <p>
      The first version of Evielution is meant to be shared intentionally. Contact details, newsletter tools, and
      broader outreach can grow in later phases.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="panel stack">
    <h2>Planned contact options</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>A simple public-facing contact method for collaborators and friends</li>
      <li>Optional outbound links to YouTube or other media homes</li>
      <li>A future custom domain email or lightweight form if needed</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="note">For now, this page acts as a placeholder until Evie chooses the right public contact method.</p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
